{"tid":1521670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"現場睇tg呀 scott scout 認證哨兵消息主頻道","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T10:52:50.000Z","uid":42246,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"640dc97eacac7e60c86def7dcf8b757db601187b","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Y9MoVd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Y9MoVd.png&h=90d2710d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場留意呀 冇Scott scout tg就快去加啦"},{"pid":"5357d4df825f70898eed176170aabea27e18272a","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8620299be609106adb5e7eae56aae928e6d9df26","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea8c03e7d488106c42e17b8c4b3e9931cb0c98e","tid":1521670,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"1752 顏色水<br />\n接仔放學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f83e5456fbd32b0d0c493b8aba137124f2ca2e","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPuc3Wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPuc3Wf.png&h=a5e5d815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只想更多人睇到消息 轉載tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1c20eef91f74b7c7cc04a10acd658fed458952","tid":1521670,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da4c91ae88628afdbed7197e6c9163c8517b7f30","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:21:25.000Z","msg":"應對 #顏料水<br />\n<br />\n特性<br />\n染料入面有稀釋左嘅 聚甲基丙烯酸甲酯 Acrylici 成份，乾左之後會好難洗甩，就咁揾水無用，一定要盡快清洗<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n包全身，完事棄裝<br />\n- 頭：先用衫 #包頭 、頭盔、眼罩、口罩 <br />\n- 頸、手：保鮮紙<br />\n- 身：全可即棄black bloc<br />\n- 鞋：即棄鞋、拎多對<br />\n- 重要：最上層要着件防水外套／雨褸<br />\n<br />\n皮膚<br />\n方法一：醋 + 水 (比例1:3)<br />\n將手浸喺醋水約5分鐘，要邊浸邊捽<br />\n<br />\n方法二：蘇打粉 + 溫水 (比例1:1)<br />\n蘇打粉水要攪勻，最好係用流動溫水邊沖邊捽，來回倒五六次就得<br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟身上面中左好多染色劑，要揾個浴缸浸落去！<br />\n<br />\n衣物<br />\n方法一：氨水（即係阿摩尼亞水）<br />\n用氨水浸15分鐘，然後再用冷水浸15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n方法二：棄掉染色衣物"},{"pid":"15aedd9af41ddd11c35c58e9f9980f59e6fb367d","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVMnGJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVMnGJK.png&h=30e54103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉載tg 更多人睇到"},{"pid":"6dbba4e7f670b935d90208caf7db5ad765b84379","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"1820，兩架水炮車準備夾攻，防暴已包抄。<br />\n<br />\n撤離路線：<br />\n<br />\n金鐘 - 盡快經PP 入地鐵 / 上斜路去英國總領事館<br />\n<br />\n灣仔 - 盡快入內街 經皇后大道東 再去銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n中環 - 直接上半山<br />\n<br />\n#逃生路線"},{"pid":"b26dc874337076dda322dc0e20fff121051b5e6f","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"#北角 <br />\n1821  書局街則魚涌方向 1長豬籠車 standby <br />\n1821 新都城炮台山方向 2衝鋒車 standby"},{"pid":"bcff829805cf403097af9394930857e5fba567e8","tid":1521670,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45e83be5f1dda7d5c00780e63020b0069398f021","tid":1521670,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ig0r8pY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fig0r8